&lt;li&gt;Desire to own all parts of a partner lifecycle, starting with profiling/recruitment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven success with sales ability and demonstrated knowledge of sales process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
